The Nikkah ceremony always leaves us in awe.

The curtain that once divided the bride and groom signifies their individual journeys until this moment.

And when it’s gently drawn aside? It’s not merely symbolic; it’s a poignant testament to two hearts embracing the start of a shared lifetime.
